Step 2: Count the number of sentences. 
There are 3 sentences in the given text.

Step 3: Calculate the average number of words per sentence.
Average words per sentence = 49 / 3 ≈ 16.33

Step 4: Count the number of long words.
1. Manipulatorerna (12 letters)
2. detektionsutrustning (20 letters)
