Total number of long words = 11.

Step 5: Calculate the LIX score.
LIX = (average words per sentence * 0.4) + ((number of long words / total number of words) * 100) * 0.2
LIX = (16.33 * 0.4) + ((11 / 49) * 100) * 0.2
LIX = 6.52 + 4.45
LIX = 10.97 ≈ 11.00

LIX = 11.00